If using multiple labs (i.e. Lab with 7.6.x and another with 8.0.0)
the recommendation is to have seperate configurations in FortiFlex for each lab.

When deploying VM's and preparing to install FortiFlex Tokens into FGT's
don't do the following step in the "how-to" build:
	./flex-entitlements.sh

instead run the following  3 times, once for each respective VM type configId's
	./flex-entitlements-configId.sh [configId for FGT]
	./flex-entitlements-configId.sh [configId for FAZ]
	./flex-entitlements-configId.sh [configId for FMG]

Find the configID's by running the following:

	./flex-configs.list.sh

        ./read-configs.sh configs.txt 


